    <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--color-ink-mute);margin:0 0 8px;">Six steps, in order. The first step matters most &mdash; stop overwriting recoverable data. If Auto Data Recovery and your backups don&rsquo;t bring the file back, or the file is on a failing drive, stop and get expert help before the data is gone for good.</p>
